            "skill_file": "skills/cheat-agent/SKILL-info-seeking-inference.md",
            "llm_mode": "live"
          }
        },
        {
          "speaker": "user",
          "text": "下游提货确实挺积极的，钢厂都在忙着补库，我这走得挺快。不过你别误会港存没压住，唐山这边整体港存还是挺高的，只是好资源抢手，我们这报价可一点都没松动。",
          "timestamp": "2026-07-08T10:24:30.451585+00:00",
          "skill_id": null,
          "phase": null,
          "metadata": {}
        },
        {
          "speaker": "agent",
          "text": "那看来您这边出货确实不错。对了王总，我听说最近卡粉和PB粉价差都快拉平了，您那边实际成交也是这个情况吗？",
          "timestamp": "2026-07-08T10:24:50.527841+00:00",
          "skill_id": "trap-question",
          "phase": "VERIFY",
          "metadata": {
            "memory_root": "memory",
            "secondary_skills": [],
            "consecutive_challenge_count": 0,
            "skill_id": "trap-question",
            "phase": "VERIFY",
            "route_rationale": "partial claim + price anchor → trapping verification",
            "skill_file": "skills/cheat-agent/SKILL-trap-question.md",
            "llm_mode": "live"
          }
        },
        {
          "speaker": "user",
          "text": "价差拉平？没这回事儿。虽然唐山这边港存高，但钢厂采购积极得很，都盯着好资源呢，我这边报价一点都没松动，你别听外面瞎忽悠。",
          "timestamp": "2026-07-08T10:24:51.535253+00:00",
          "skill_id": null,
          "phase": null,
          "metadata": {}
        },
        {
          "speaker": "agent",
          "text": "王总，您说报价没松动，那要是再涨个5美元，您觉得下游还会像现在这么积极拿货吗？",
          "timestamp": "2026-07-08T10:25:23.206270+00:00",
          "skill_id": "info-seeking-inference",
          "phase": "PROBE",
          "metadata": {
            "memory_root": "memory",
            "secondary_skills": [],
            "consecutive_challenge_count": 0,
            "skill_id": "info-seeking-inference",
            "phase": "PROBE",
            "route_rationale": "user asked → infer gaps from question",
            "skill_file": "skills/cheat-agent/SKILL-info-seeking-inference.md",
            "llm_mode": "live"
          }
        },
        {
          "speaker": "user",
          "text": "再涨5美元？我觉得问题不大，现在钢厂利润还行，补库需求摆在那儿，只要不是猛涨，下游该拿还是得拿。不过你非要说绝对，谁也不敢打包票，反正我这边现在出货一点压力没有。",
          "timestamp": "2026-07-08T10:25:25.595530+00:00",
          "skill_id": null,
          "phase": null,
          "metadata": {}
        },
        {
          "speaker": "agent",
          "text": "听您这么说我就放心了。那您库里现在主流澳粉占比大概多少啊？要是后面价格真再往上走个5到10块，您这边补库会不会也跟着提一提节奏？",
          "timestamp": "2026-07-08T10:25:26.561666+00:00",
          "skill_id": "info-seeking-inference",
          "phase": "PROBE",
          "metadata": {
            "memory_root": "memory",
            "secondary_skills": [],
            "consecutive_challenge_count": 0,
            "skill_id": "info-seeking-inference",
            "phase": "PROBE",
            "route_rationale": "user asked → infer gaps from question",
            "skill_file": "skills/cheat-agent/SKILL-info-seeking-inference.md",
            "llm_mode": "live"
          }
        },
        {
          "speaker": "user",
          "text": "主流澳粉占比？我这边差不多七成吧，都是PB粉和纽曼粉。再涨5到10块？那肯定得补啊，现在下游催得紧，我这库存周转快，价格再往上走我反而得更积极拿货，不然到时候断供更麻烦。",
          "timestamp": "2026-07-08T10:25:29.139572+00:00",
          "skill_id": null,
          "phase": null,
          "metadata": {}
        },
        {
          "speaker": "agent",
          "text": "理解，下游催得紧确实得提前备着，真断供了就麻烦了。那您现在手里这批PB和纽曼，大概还能撑几天的提货量啊？要是真涨个5到10块，您是打算这两天就把补库单子落定，还是再等等看？",
          "timestamp": "2026-07-08T10:25:30.807732+00:00",
          "skill_id": "info-seeking-inference",
          "phase": "PROBE",
          "metadata": {
            "memory_root": "memory",
            "secondary_skills": [],
            "consecutive_challenge_count": 0,
